accessibility.text: “I am an old man now, and when I die and go to heaven there are two matters on which I hope for enlightenment:\u2028\u2028 One is quantum electrodynamics, \u2028and the other is the turbulent motion of fluids.
And about the former I am rather optimistic.”
“Turbulence is the most important unsolved problem of classical physics”
